<p><strong>Referral</strong></p>
<p>Please email your referral to <a href="mailto:reception@woolcock.org.au">reception@woolcock.org.au</a> prior to your appointment. Please note that your referral is valid for 36 months.</p>
<p><strong>Payment for your consultation:</strong></p>
<p>The cost of your consultation is $180.00. Additional procedures or services requested after your consultation (Mandibular Advancement Splint or MAS) will start from $2,120. We accept EFTPOS, credit cards including AMEX without surcharge (no Diners Club), or cash. You will be given a receipt which can be used to claim partial reimbursement from your private health fund if your cover allows. You will be provided a quotation of professional fees at your appointment.</p>
<p>Please note that this is a private clinic and Dr Donegan doesn&rsquo;t Bulk Bill.</p>
<p>Approval documentation from your Insurer needs to be provided in the case of a Workers&rsquo; Compensation or Third-Party Claim. If not supplied, payment will need to be made on the day by the patient.</p>
<p><strong>Appopintment confirmation and cancellation fees</strong></p>
<p>We expect you to confirm your appointment in a timely manner and have te right to reduce it from 60 minutes to 15 minutes if we do not hear from you.</p>
<p>When a patient cancels their appointment or does not attend without giving notice, they prevent another patient from being seen.&nbsp; Therefore, your Doctor requires a 48-hour cancellation notice for any appointment changes. A charge of $100 will apply for any appointment changes that may occur without appropriate notice.&nbsp;</p>
